<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE WEEK AHEAD: LILLEHAMMER; LET THE GAMES BEGIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Winter Olympic Games begin Saturday in this Norwegian sports resort. The 
Lillehammer Games start a new sequence in the Olympic schedule.Previously both 
the Winter and Summer Olympics were held in the same year. The last Winter 
Games took place in 1992 at Albertville, France, and the 1994 resumption begins 
a cycle in which each even-numbered year will see either a winter or summer 
festival. The 1996 Summer Games will take place in Atlanta, and Calgary will 
host the 1998 Winter festival. 
</P>
<P>
 These Games have been marked by controversy even before the opening ceremony, 
notably the drama involving the American women figure skaters.  
</P>
<P>
 But as the XVIIth Games approach, Lillehammer appeared to be taking a 
fun-filled approach to the festival, anticipating the arrival of 100,000 
tourists a day with bulging wallets. 
</P>
</TEXT>
