<TEXT>
<P>
 Merger to Create Health Care Power: T2 Medical Inc., Curaflex Health Services 
Inc., Healthinfusion Inc. and Medisys Inc. said they will merge to become the 
second-largest U.S. home infusion company. The new company, called Coram 
Healthcare Corp., would have combined revenue of $500 million and a combined 
market value of $550 million. 
