</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020894-0123 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 011476 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 8, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 1; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
