 Calabasas High School 
</P>
<P>
 22855 Mulholland Highway 
</P>
<P>
 Fillmore 
</P>
<P>
 St. Francis Church Community Hall 
</P>
<P>
 1058 Ventura St. 
</P>
<P>
 Glendale 
