Ojai 2.15 6.84 13.12 Oxnard 1.05 4.06 8.39 Piru 0.69 3.98 9.93 Santa Paula 1.20 
4.98 10.23 Simi Valley 0.73 4.14 8.19 Thousand Oaks 0.74 4.29 8.82 Ventura 
County Government Center 1.69 5.08 9.28  
</P>
