<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL ROUNDUP: FLAMEMASTER, PERFECTDATA RAISE STAKE IN PERMABYTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Sun Valley chemicals concern Flamemaster Corp. and PerfectData Corp., a Simi 
Valley maker of office cleaning products, said they raised their joint stake in 
PermaByte Inc. from 55% to 70%. 
</P>
<P>
 PermaByte, based in San Diego, makes computer floppy disks, disk holders and 
custom-made parts for various office products. PermaByte reported sales of 
about $4.4 million last year. Flamemaster and its affiliates own 33% of 
PerfectData's outstanding common stock. 
</P>
</TEXT>
